OL,3,CBurnley owners complete the purchase
OL,4,Cof a majority stake in Espanyol
OL,6,FThe owners of Burnley have completed
OL,7,Fthe purchase of a majority stake in
OL,8,FSpanish club Espanyol.
OL,10,FVelocity Sports Partners, led by
OL,11,FClarets chairman Alan Pace, announced
OL,12,Fthe acquisition on Thursday following
OL,13,Fa period of due diligence.
OL,15,FIt says it intends to "invest in world-
OL,16,Fclass academies and infrastructure, to
OL,17,Fachieve long-term footballing success
OL,18,Fon and off the field" at the Barcelona-
OL,19,Fbased side.
