OL,3,CBurnley owners complete the purchase
OL,4,Cof a majority stake in Espanyol
OL,6,FPace, managing partner of ALK Capital,
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement: "Our role is not
OL,8,Fto replace legacy but to build upon
OL,9,Fit, with care, with clarity, and with
OL,10,Fpurpose.
OL,12,F"This is not about ownership; it's
OL,13,Fabout stewardship. Burnley will remain
OL,14,FBurnley. Espanyol will remain Espanyol.
OL,16,F"Each club will retain its own
OL,17,Fleadership, identity, independence and
OL,18,Fdecision-making, run by its own
OL,19,Fpeople, for its own supporters."
